Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, rsync, aptitude, gdebi, aria2, duplicity
#Recommends: 
Description: Utility to backup and restore PPAs and packages.
 Command line utility to simplify re-installation of software packages
 after upgrading/re-installing Ubuntu-based distributions.
 Provides options to backup and restore PPAs, installed packages,
 downloaded packages in APT cache, icons, themes
 and application settings.
